SUMMARY:Fireside Chat: How is AI Changing the World of Work?
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260622T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260622T174500
DESCRIPTION:This session will explore how AI is reshaping workplaces and corporate strategies: • AI in Engineering and Operations: How organizations are applying AI in product design, software development, and operational workflows. • Impact on Job Roles: Which positions are evolving, which tasks are being automated, and the new skills employees need. • Corporate Approaches: Strategies for upskilling, workforce planning, and integrating AI responsibly. • Practical Examples: Showcasing companies successfully\nRSVP: https://www.unopensource.org/agenda
LOCATION:New York, NY
END:VEVENT
