UID:evt-2026-040@osweekplus.nyc
SUMMARY:Turning Global Commitments into Action
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260624T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260624T114500
DESCRIPTION:The Global Digital Compact and the Fourth International Conference on Financing for Development established ambitious commitments on digital public infrastructure. This panel brings together ministers, multilateral development banks, and practitioners to take stock of how those commitments are being translated into concrete action at country and regional level. Speakers will share first-hand experiences and identify what it will take to sustain momentum through 2027 and beyond\nRSVP: https://www.unopensource.org/agenda
LOCATION:New York, NY
END:VEVENT
